    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and have been regularly serviced, the car shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior upholstery shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. It has been a reliable commuter, but it is not a showpiece; expect a solid mechanical foundation with cosmetic imperfections that reflect its history.",
