    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this extraordinary vehicle, preserved in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. This specimen exhibits no signs of wear, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in a state of absolute preservation. Meticulously maintained to the highest standards, its mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation are indistinguishable from a new delivery. This is an uncompromising opportunity for the sophisticated buyer seeking a vehicle of investment-grade caliber.",
      "price": 46500.0,
