      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a collector-grade 2013 BMW M3 Coupe (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This final-year specimen is in superlative condition, showcasing factory-original paint with no evidence of road rash or swirls. The high-revving powerplant delivers a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline, supported by a meticulously maintained M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This ZCP-equipped example features the enhanced Electronic Damper Control (EDC) mapping and a 10mm lowered suspension geometry for superior turn-in response. Preventative maintenance is current, including recent rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service to ensure long-term mechanical reliability. The cockpit remains in showroom state, with no bolster wear on the Novillo leather or degradation of the carbon-fiber trim. Full service documentation is available, and pre-purchase inspections at a BMW specialist are encouraged to confirm its mechanical excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
